text: Oksana Kiselyova born 30 May 1992, in Baku,Волейболистка Оксана Киселева: «В моем гардеробе преобладают спортивные вещи» Azerbaijan) is an Azerbaijani volleyball player. She is 177 cm tall and plays as libero. She plays for Lokomotiv Baku. Kiselyova is a current member of the Azerbaijan women's national volleyball team. Kiselyova is married to Azerbaijani football player Farid Guliyev.Лучший бомбардир чемпионата Азербайджана женится на волейболистке национальной команды (ФОТО) ==Clubs== Kiselyova has played for the following clubs, all in Azerbaijan: * Azerrail Baku (2006–2012, 2013-2014) * Azeryol Baku (2012–2013) * Lokomotiv Baku (2014–) ==Awards== ===Club=== * 2006–07 Azerbaijan Women's Volleyball Super League - 16px Champion, with Azerrail Baku * 2007–08 Azerbaijan Women's Volleyball Super League - 16px Champion, with Azerrail Baku * 2008–09 Azerbaijan Women's Volleyball Super League - 16px Runner-Up, with Azerrail Baku * 2010–11 Azerbaijan Women's Volleyball Super League - 16px Runner-Up, with Azerrail Baku * 2014–15 Azerbaijan Women's Volleyball Super League - 16px Runner-Up, with Lokomotiv Baku ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Azerbaijani women's volleyball players Category:Sportspeople from Baku Category:European Games competitors for Azerbaijan Category:Volleyball players at the 2015 European Games Category:Liberos
